{"abstract":[{"text":"Radio button is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Radio button that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a Radio button to be displayed.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift"},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading"},{"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_OrangeCom